# PyFixFmt

Python Format Fixer.


### Instructions

To run:

```
$ # Recommended way, since it should work from wherever it's installed
$ python -m pyfixfmt --file-glob <your file glob here> --verbose

$ # Or, since I'm a nice guy
$ python pyfixfmt --file-glob <your file glob here> --verbose

```

